          version="5.0-subset Scilab"
          xml:id="XcosMenuSaveAsInterfFunc">
  <refnamediv>
    <refname>Save_as_Interf_Func</refname>
    <refpurpose>Menu: Save the diagram as a new Scicos block.</refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsection>
    <title>Description</title>
    <para>
      Select the <literal>Save as Interf. Func.</literal> menu item to save the
      diagram as a new Scicos block. A Scilab function is generated
      and saved in a file with ".sci" extension. File name and path
      are to be set in a "File menu" dialog.
    </para>
  </refsection>

</refentry>
